Description: Parrot Security OS 6.3 (Lorikeet) for Termux
 Provides Parrot Security OS 6.3 environment within Termux using
 PRoot containerization. Includes comprehensive security tools,
 penetration testing utilities, and forensic analysis packages
 without requiring device root access.
